{"tid":1151454,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"watchOS 6更新將使Apple Watch更能獨立運作使用","createTime":"2019-05-12T14:23:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T01:51:24.000Z","uid":50534,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c506a961c6a0b32b4b448c02eb0d8a8ebb4f1115","tid":1151454,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T14:23:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mashdigi.com/watchos-6-will-let-apple-watch-being-more-stanalone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmashdigi.com%2Fwatchos-6-will-let-apple-watch-being-more-stanalone%2F&d=gf59OkzbMHBVvJ2bZZ4HagzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=ef7c3977\" target=\"_blank\">https://mashdigi.com/watchos-6-will-let-apple-watch-being-more-stanalone/</a><br />\n新版watchOS 6預期將會讓Apple Watch變得更容易獨立運作，例如將會加入全新App Store項目，讓使用者能直接透過手錶上的App Store選擇適合Apple Watch使用app，另外也會加入更多錶面與可顯示內容選項。<br />\n<br />\nwatchOS 6預期加入功能：<br />\n<br />\n全新獨立的App Store，相比過往透過iPhone上的Watch app選項操作安裝，未來使用者將能直接在Apple Watch上完成安裝App。<br />\n新增獨立語音備忘錄app，讓使用者能直接透過Apple Watch錄製錄音記事項目。<br />\n將能與iPhone上的Animoji、Memoji內容整合，並且可傳送給他人。<br />\n健康應用項目將會加入可提醒服藥時間的「Dose」，以及針對女性提供記錄月經週期的「Cycles」。<br />\n新款錶面，包含依照使用者挑選顏色呈現的「Gradient (梯度)」，新款大字體錶面「X-Large」，以羅馬數字與阿拉伯數字混搭的「California」，重新設計的「Solar Analog (太陽)」，而新版「Infograph Subdial」錶面則可顯示更多複雜內容資訊。<br />\n操作介面中，蘋果也預期因應新版Apple Watch錶面螢幕面積提昇，因此將會加入更多資訊顯示項目，例如顯示有聲讀物閱讀進度、顯示助聽器電池殘量，以及外部噪音值與天氣資訊等。"},{"pid":"9d7f4d9d93c6c8cc3fe631b8c57f925d751fd278","tid":1151454,"uid":109383,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T14:25:09.000Z","msg":"可能下一代粒U勁好撚多...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bed7d6ce0d6dc0a01ca5a56a9ba750c7ea1cbd4","tid":1151454,"uid":191815,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T14:27:28.000Z","msg":"下代佢出圓面嘅我立即課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a367cd66fcbe0a943441329c4c0f6a17d979b9","tid":1151454,"uid":109383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score